model.gameMaze.solver

Class Maze

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.gameMaze.solver.Maze
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Maze
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Maze class - holds a data member of type int[][] that represents a 2D matrix that is our maze. Generates the maze randomly where the size of the maze is between 3-22 (rows or columns).
    Author:
    Tzelon Machluf and Jasmine Nouriel
